{"tid":1373351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請入黎 遠程單兵武器 需普及化","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:47:26.000Z","uid":165234,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a72b7d344027c359367d0f99a0f9128fb85fad88","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LPGLtY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LPGLtY.jpg&h=813558f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先氣球平，墨水墨汁平<br />\n<br />\n加墨汁同埋辣椒醬 可以現場pump墨水入氣球<br />\n<br />\n可以投向黑警 鄉黑到 村口門牌 干擾同羞辱佢地<br />\n<br />\n如果個個示威者都配備投擲彈嘅話 個局勢會好唔同<br />\n<br />\n今次元朗 我地做得好差 當義士係condom <br />\n<br />\n不過記住 羅馬並非一日建成 我地要keep住進步<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命 <br />\n<br />\n守護香港，責無旁貸</span>"},{"pid":"86d90a7ce0c7f6bf7783e14048cc8b484f673aec","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da83c52e60726ecefc08bbd28d83c8efed920cec","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:15:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2760f78e9dde8a0e18ea0f7e46ad484e15c06c3d","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f87dd3a14d017ec1ff5d6efabc4af191fdb2a17","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"814493cb0887fbe31caee4794cfc152994349d25","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49543508df3764f5ebeaf4f309df34189129af94","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52abe417b27d84b1f45f3ade1f6d896ee2826c64","tid":1373351,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15: